.TH NORTHSTAR 1 "July 2026" "northstar" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
northstar \- minimalist GTK 4 web browser with an original engine
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B northstar
.RI [ options ]
.RI [ URL ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Northstar is a web browser written from scratch in C, with a GTK 4
user interface and a libcurl network stack. Its HTML, CSS, and
JavaScript engine is an original implementation \(em it is not based
on Gecko, WebKit, or Blink. Pages render in a sandboxed renderer
process; the browser supports HTML5, modern CSS, modern JavaScript,
WebAssembly, and inline MPEG-1 video playback.
.PP
When started without arguments, Northstar opens its start page.
Passing a URL opens that page in a new tab.
.SH OPTIONS
Northstar accepts the standard GTK 4 command-line options.
.SH SEE ALSO
Project homepage:
.UR https://github.com/nordstjernen-web/northstar-browser
.UE
